{"meta":{"version":1},"name":"Shooter++","source":{"language":"V2","code":"// robot 'shooter++'\n// v2 version of the classic shooter\nstate main() {\n    def angle\n    // use a loop instead of re-iterating the state. its much faster.\n    while true {\n        def r = @radar(angle)\n        if r < 0 {\n            @fire(angle, abs(r))\n        } else {\n            angle = angle + 7\n        }\n    }\n}\n"}}